            <p className="mt-3 text-[14px] font-semibold leading-7 text-[#51465a]">Families from Delhi, Noida, Gurgaon, Faridabad, Ghaziabad and across India connect with Manovaidya for Mild Cognitive Impairment \(MCI\) Treatment, Healthy Brain Ageing Guidance and Senior Mental Health Support through both online and in-clinic consultations.</p>
